OL,3,CCouple launch exhibition to highlight
OL,4,Ctown's musical history
OL,6,FITV News' Akshay Raja went to meet the
OL,7,Fcouple hoping to shed light on their
OL,8,Ftown's music history.
OL,10,FA married couple are hoping to
OL,11,Fhighlight the rich music history of
OL,12,Ftheir hometown through a new
OL,13,Fexhibition.
OL,15,FJohn and Rosemary Barratt created the
OL,16,FStockport Music Story to show how the
OL,17,FGreater Manchester town is full of
OL,18,Fartists that have "really made an
OL,19,Fimpact on the music scene".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
