OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778073066
OL,3,CCouple launch exhibition to highlight
OL,4,Ctown's musical history
OL,6,FStockport has a rich musical legacy,
OL,7,Fas demonstrated most recently by the
OL,8,Fsuccess of local band Blossoms.
OL,10,FBut the town's pivotal role in the
OL,11,Fmusic scene is not restricted to the
OL,12,Fsuccess of artists born there.
OL,14,FJimi Hendrix, Pink Floyd and David
OL,15,FBowie are just some of the names who
OL,16,Fhave played in Stockport's most iconic
OL,17,Fvenues, including Manor Lounge, The
OL,18,FTabernacle, and The Sinking Ship.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778073066
OL,3,CCouple launch exhibition to highlight
OL,4,Ctown's musical history
OL,6,FThis history is not widely known,
OL,7,Fsomething which John and Rosemary are
OL,8,Fhoping to change.
OL,10,FJohn and Rosemary Barratt started the
OL,11,FStockport Music Story during lockdown
OL,12,Fto celebrate their hometown's creative
OL,13,Fheritage.
OL,15,FThey have now partnered with Stockport
OL,16,FStation to install a collection of
OL,17,Fpieces by local artists in the station
OL,18,Ftunnel. These artworks shine a light
OL,19,Fon the town's key musical moments and
OL,20,Ffigures.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
