OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778073066
OL,3,CCouple launch exhibition to highlight
OL,4,Ctown's musical history
OL,6,FJohn Barratt says the project
OL,7,F"celebrates mavericks. It celebrates
OL,8,Fpeople from the town who have really
OL,9,Fmade an impact on the music scene."
OL,11,FOne such maverick is Dee
OL,12,FChristopholus; the frontman and lead
OL,13,Fsinger of Wimple Winch.
OL,15,FWhen Hendrix performed at Stockport's
OL,16,FSinking Ship in February 1967, Wimple
OL,17,FWinch were the support act.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
