OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778073066
OL,3,CCouple launch exhibition to highlight
OL,4,Ctown's musical history
OL,6,FJohn Sweeney attended that gig. He was
OL,7,Fonly a teenager at the time, but
OL,8,Fremembers the night clearly: "If you
OL,9,Fthink of Hendrix in a tiny little
OL,10,Fcave, with 100 people squashed in
OL,11,Ftogether- the noise was just amazing.
OL,13,F"It was just one of those hair-raising
OL,14,Fmoments when you walked in, and
OL,15,FHendrix got onto the stage.
OL,17,F"He had to come through the audience
OL,18,Fto get onto the stage because there
OL,19,Fwas no back entrance to it, it was
OL,20,Flike a cave basically- so, yeah, it
OL,21,Fwas an unforgettable night."
OL,26,@pD@^OUuD@AOUyD@AOU}D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
