PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778073066
OL,3,CCouple launch exhibition to highlight
OL,4,Ctown's musical history
OL,6,FOnly months after this performance,
OL,7,Fthe Sinking Ship burned down. It never
OL,8,Fopened again.
OL,10,FFor Christopholus, who lived above the
OL,11,Fclub and escaped through the window,
OL,12,Fthis marked the beginning of the end
OL,13,Fof his band.
OL,15,FBut he believes the work of the
OL,16,FStockport Music Story is keeping its
OL,17,Flegacy alive. "It's John Barratt and
OL,18,FRosemary who've done it all, you know
OL,19,Fwhat I mean.
OL,26,@yD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
