OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1778073066
OL,3,CCouple launch exhibition to highlight
OL,4,Ctown's musical history
OL,6,F"They've kept the enthusiasm going...
OL,7,Fthey're fantastic".
OL,9,FSweeney reiterates this point: "John
OL,10,Fand Rosemary are doing an incredible
OL,11,Fjob, bringing to the attention of
OL,12,Feveryone what a great scene it was in
OL,13,FStockport and how many famous places
OL,14,Fand people have come out of the
OL,15,FStockport area".
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@RO]qD@`OUwD@OO]
